Title: AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE BARRIO OF PAYOMPON, MUNICIPALITY OF SABLAYAN, PROVINCE OF MINDORO, TO THAT OF BUENAVISTA.(awÞhi(
Data:
[ Commonwealth Act No. 28, September 08, 1936 ]
AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE BARRIO OF PAYOMPON, MUNICIPALITY OF SABLAYAN, PROVINCE OF MINDORO, TO THAT OF BUENAVISTA.(awÞhi(
Be it enacted by the National Assembly of the Philippines:
Section 1. The name of the barrio of Payompon, municipality of Sablayan, Province of Mindoro, is hereby changed to that of Buenavista.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Enacted, without Executive approval, September 8, 1936.
